<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Refund Completed</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #16a34a; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f8fafc; }
        .refund-details { background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .appointment-details { background-color: #e2e8f0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #666; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Refund Completed</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{patientName}},</p>
            
            <p>Your refund has been successfully processed.</p>

            <div class="refund-details">
                <h3>Refund Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Amount:</strong> ${{refund.amount}}</p>
                <p><strong>Refund ID:</strong> {{refund.refundId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Processed Date:</strong> {{refund.processedDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Status:</strong> Completed</p>
            </div>

            <div class="appointment-details">
                <h3>Original Appointment Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Doctor:</strong> Dr. {{doctorName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Scheduled Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</p>
                <p><strong>Cancellation Reason:</strong> {{cancellationReason}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>The refund has been processed to your original payment method. It may take a few business days to appear in your account.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© 2025 MediConnect System</p>
            <p>Timestamp: {{timestamp}}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>